{"tid":2091541,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"未必可行，忽發其想的保護","createTime":"2020-07-02T17:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T17:00:28.000Z","uid":284463,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56245e67e1879980079e82ea220c222cdf0a29ef","tid":2091541,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"每當有手足比傳媒影到，要即時離開嘅時候，我唔知有能力嘅幫手一齊買機票有冇用，但係中共肺炎底下，呢個可能係其中一個方法保護到手足。<br />\n<br />\n大約係有能力有錢嘅就買，做戲做全套去埋機場，幾千至一萬保護一條人命咁。<br />\n<br />\n但可行性算低，所以睇下咁多位手足有咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">P牌淨係得一日一po，只好講埋其他嘢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n無力感愈嚟愈大，但我知有其他人一定比我更慘，安穩我地未必一時半刻有，更何況如果要安穩，大家都唔會選擇揀呢條路。<br />\n要來嘅始終要來，你若放棄，誰衛我城？咁多位手足加油，大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘初衷</span></span>，一步一步好似骨牌咁，終有一日會完，而個結果都會好靚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望大家唔好放棄，繼續光復我地嘅香港，一個屬於自己嘅時代革命。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a724d5657779a82e45d8c9e818c267771fb5ceb","tid":2091541,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"其實係可行"},{"pid":"7e49bf069867a63cbaa735ec589baf7f117b72d3","tid":2091541,"uid":284463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Yaf7zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Yaf7zR.jpg&h=b0198b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋真係好撚鍾意香港<br />\nWeReallyFuckingLoveHongKong"},{"pid":"6607be811040d6b58bbc22ff7ef48b0e0f027b96","tid":2091541,"uid":284463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a724d5657779a82e45d8c9e818c267771fb5ceb","tid":2091541,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"